org.deeplearning4j.ui.stats.api

Interface StatsReport

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaStatsReport, SbeStatsReport

    public interface StatsReport
extends Persistable
    StatsReport: An interface for storing and serializing update information (such as scores, parameter histograms etc) for use in the StatsListener
